            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2026年7月21日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">「國家隊」托A股 恒指急彈洗頹勢<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/07/21/4461278_402e049b373982a2ac3b921c9e53a4a3.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/07/21/4461278_402e049b373982a2ac3b921c9e53a4a3_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/07/21/4461278_402e049b373982a2ac3b921c9e53a4a3.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2026/07/21/4461278_402e049b373982a2ac3b921c9e53a4a3.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n內地各方多措並舉維穩股市，「國家隊」現入市托A股手影，刺激恒指昨反彈580點，在亞太區股市受壓下，與國指雙雙跑出。分析認為，A股兩融餘額（孖展借貸和借貨沽空）連日下跌迫使當局出手，惟A股本輪跌市與基本面無關，港股昨逆市急漲，但要走出谷底仍需更強催化劑配合。\n以韓股為首的亞洲科技股近日大幅震盪，滬指日...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
